import React from "react";

export default ({ onClick }) => (
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="24"
    height="24"
    fill="none"
    onClick={onClick}
    stroke="currentColor"
    strokeLinecap="round"
    strokeLinejoin="round"
    strokeWidth="2"
    className="feather feather-smile"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
  >
    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
    <path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2" />
    <path d="M9 9L9.01 9" />
    <path d="M15 9L15.01 9" />
  </svg>
);
